Package: UCSCutils
Title: Low-level utilities to retrieve data from the UCSC Genome Browser
Description: A set of low-level utilities to retrieve data from the UCSC
	Genome Browser. Data is accessed via the UCSC REST API or by querying
	the UCSC MySQL server directly.
biocViews: Infrastructure, Annotation, GenomeAnnotation, DataImport
URL: https://bioconductor.org/packages/UCSCutils
BugReports: https://github.com/Bioconductor/UCSCutils/issues
Version: 0.0.2
License: Artistic-2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
